name: Unpainted Thai Airways 777-300ER Rejected Takeoff at Paine Field ᴴᴰ
description:
Hello everyone, this is a Boeing 777-300ER destined for Thai Airways doing a Rejected Takeoff Test (RTO) at Paine Field. This bird is still in the primer, and is to be the 8th 77W in Thai's fleet. Listen to those GE-90s! -TKQ has since been delivered, and is now operating with Thai Airways.

Thanks for watching, please comment, rate, and subscribe! More videos are coming soon.
